➜国内都有哪些有特色的古塔?
https://daily.zhihu.com/story/9726554	83291
<div><div><div>
<img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f5d0774a5f2d649f40b06673a9fe3da9_is.jpg">
<span>男爵兔，</span><span>阿拉伯/斯瓦希里/宗教/东方文学/相声/民谣作词</span>
